Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 我什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了拖累大家的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满心的杂念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在刚才的格斗训练中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你否定自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你也没有任何帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小巴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别这么消沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢开朗的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\an7\3c&H000000&\bord1\pos(480.075,336.333)}#07 银发 金发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一望无际的蔚蓝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样 茱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 呐 集训所会是个怎样的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了新的泳衣来 超可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 透流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.73,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的海滨夏令营却…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷热再加上晕船 会这样也无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也不会是什么正经的海滨夏令营
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在休息下会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常地舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉就像是小动物一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗 穗高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茱莉没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 比起待在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吹吹风似乎能让她舒服点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是的 看上去很舒服的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在那里很热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这边来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就恭敬不如从命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 透流 月见让我们都过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有件事要向大家宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位从这里游到集训所所在的那个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游过去… 你说真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便作为特训 请大家穿着制服游过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为「超越者」 这种程度必须轻松克服才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要仔细地观察实验动物的生态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终目的地是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位于岛中心的建筑 这次的集训所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 打起精神 GO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 之前期末曾有过「升华之仪」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那提升了等级的人姑且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能提升等级的废物动物们 别拖「绊双刃」的后腿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 赶紧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 茱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖 但是我们落后了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 很快就能追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 透流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为选泳衣所以来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去了 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 你未来的伴侣来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦 露出这种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是容易害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请离远点 透流是我的「绊双刃」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 难道你不会游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「绊双刃」的话 就别拖透流的后腿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这种话的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点去岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就比比谁先到岛上吧 透流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着制服果然很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的压倒性胜利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 透流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 不过稍微让我休息会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着湿透的内衣很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在你衣服干了之前让我休息会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去那边晾干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走太远了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是天然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样比较舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 莉莉丝你也很热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意 是我自愿这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 要是你还是觉得过意不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报答一下我也行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 只要是我能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 作为奖励我要个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你帮我遮阳光了 心意我领了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 茱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本想晾干的 结果被风吹走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流 盯着我看可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 雅 马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉我总是在拖小巴的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家已经到很前面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我们照着自己的节奏走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 小巴 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小巴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的「绊双刃」 雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你否定自己就相当于否定了作为「绊双刃」的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所选择的「绊双刃」 只有穗高雅一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 在这里把海水的盐分给洗掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里好像就是集训所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天暗了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们抓紧时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊胜于无嘛 之后的路光脚走会很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 透流 不愧是我未来的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是做我的「绊双刃」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流 这边的路看起来更好走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是苦无 这岛上莫非有忍者居住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是焰牙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 对方更占地利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九重君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焰牙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里埋伏我们 是为了把树作为围笼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没叫你救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖 是我自愿这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是空间再大点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 请迅速跳上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焰牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Level 3的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 表演时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 居然使用焰牙 这些家伙究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊万里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 透流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 差不多可以把手拿开了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流 真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本校的各位学生 欢迎来到昊陵学园分校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突如其来的模拟战 粗暴的欢迎方式想必吓到大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样才符合昊陵学园的海滨夏令营
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以从今天开始的共同训练 请大家多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到还有分校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初也感到很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在入学仪式的「资格之仪」中输掉的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要愿意便可进入这个分校就读
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然环境和训练都很严酷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但每天都很充实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那透流你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的食欲都好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉瞬间就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是游泳又是对战 大家都饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不嫌弃的话吃我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流的香肠真是又热又大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是两只手都腾不出来 让你喂我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 味道不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 为什么非要让你来喂我吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 再次一口 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别无视我的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我误会您了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾认为您是个很冷酷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 您并未抛弃伊万里他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像误会什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做只是因为黎明机构需要那些人才
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本谈不上感谢一说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 保重 九重透流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所求之物只有一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的一切就是为了达到绝对双刃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的战斗真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是本校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没有那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就像她们说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为雅是我引以为傲的「绊双刃」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿点吃的来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九 九重君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 我刚听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了救橘表现得非常出色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时只是顾不了那么多了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那是因为九重君…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直以来都有九重君在旁鼓励
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然是喜欢九重君的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装钢的调整已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩最后一个阶段了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在此之前我还有个素材想要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要我去执行这个作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需向上面的人报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他们也只是想知道这东西的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说把测试的结果告诉他们就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测试… 所谓的品评和被品评吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么此次的作战名是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就取名为品评会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(468.388,437)\fs21}Selection
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样在海滨夏令营的这一周就能和透流一起睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:22:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 透流
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过今天的事我得到了个很好的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做事要有备无患
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮我带着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透流 拉开看有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 饶了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 Selection
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有衣服滑落的福利镜头哦
