Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:29.24,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}ひらり　くるり　はらり　ふわり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.08,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}あわい　しろい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:32.81,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}ふたりの未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:34.69,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}ゆれる　はずむ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.49,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}うかぶ　しずむ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.31,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}はねる　ならぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.15,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}こころのリズム
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:43.92,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}きっかけは少しのおしゃべり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:47.31,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}考えがまさかのイコール
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:50.92,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}きっかけはぶつかりあいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:54.57,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}ちょっとだけ遠回りかもね…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:22:00.68,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\3c&H43D5F3&}けんかしたら分かる　はじめ　見えなかったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:22:00.38,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}仲良くなりたいな　なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:07.25,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}それは甘いアップルティーの味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:15.70,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}さみしいとか いつでも考えたことなかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:22.24,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}気づいちゃったわたし きみがいないとさみしいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:25.16,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}明日には　Happy Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.87,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}明日にも　Happy Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.38,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}いつの日か　Happy Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:35.98,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}いつの日も　Happy Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:29.24,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}轻快地 旋转地 悄悄地 轻轻地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.08,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}淡淡的 白白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:32.81,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}我们两人的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:34.69,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}摇摆不定 高涨激动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.49,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}扶摇而上 低潮而下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.31,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}悸动不已 心平气和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.15,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}奏响心跳的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:43.92,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}邂逅来自短暂的闲谈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:47.31,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}我们的想法竟完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:50.92,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}邂逅来自互相的争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:54.57,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}让我们的友情绕了远路…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:22:00.68,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\3c&H43D5F3&}争吵了之后便明白了 最初所没有察觉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:22:00.38,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}想要变成知心朋友 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:07.25,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}那是甘甜的苹果茶香味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:15.70,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}寂寞什么的我从未想过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:22.24,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}回过神来却发现 没有你在我是如此寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:25.16,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}明天要 Happy Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.87,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}明天也 Happy Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.38,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}总有一天要 Happy Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:35.98,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3}每一天都要 Happy Happy
